    {
      "paragraph_name": "RECEIVE-PAULST-SCREEN",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph receives data from the COPAU0A screen. It executes a CICS RECEIVE command, retrieving data from the COPAU0A mapset ('COPAU00') into the COPAU0AI map. It also retrieves the RESP and RESP2 codes into WS-RESP-CD and WS-REAS-CD, respectively. This paragraph is responsible for capturing user input from the screen. The paragraph consumes the COPAU0A screen and writes to COPAU0AI, WS-RESP-CD, and WS-REAS-CD. It does not call any other paragraphs or programs.",
