      "paragraph_name": "GETCUSTDATA-BYCUST",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph retrieves the customer record based on the customer ID. It moves the customer ID (XREF-CUST-ID) to WS-CARD-RID-CUST-ID. It then executes a CICS READ command to read the CUSTOMER-RECORD from the VSAM file specified by WS-CUSTFILENAME, using WS-CARD-RID-CUST-ID-X as the key. If the read is successful (DFHRESP(NORMAL)), it continues processing. If the record is not found (DFHRESP(NOTFND)), it constructs an error message and calls SEND-PAULST-SCREEN to display the message. If any other error occurs, it sets WS-ERR-FLG to 'Y', constructs an error message, and calls SEND-PAULST-SCREEN. The paragraph consumes XREF-CUST-ID and writes to CUSTOMER-RECORD, WS-MESSAGE, and COPAU0AI. It also uses WS-CUSTFILENAME to determine the dataset name.",
